        "setup": "Request API access via the [CB Insights Developer Portal signup form](https://api-docs.cbinsights.com/portal/signup). After your email is validated, CB Insights provides your `clientId` and `clientSecret` for the trial environment. The API reference also says production credentials are provided by your Customer Success Manager or by contacting [info@cbinsights.com](mailto:info@cbinsights.com).",
